deck: A human with temporal awareness rescued by the Guardians of the Galaxy from the Badoon.
description:
Origin

Geena Drake is a human from Earth captured by the conquering Badoon and imprisoned. She was rescued by the Guardians of the Galaxy because Starhawk believes her to be a vital key to stopping a bigger threat than the Badoon. Time itself is contracting and collapsing, forcing the Guardians to continue fighting the war with the Badoon.

Geena is able to see these temporal shifts and remembers previous events after shifts occur. She would later discover that it is because she is a singularity in the multiverse.
